commentTextItems.html: and it's done! A low full toss as Usman clips it past the midwicket region

commentPostTextItems.html: That's all from this match. Do join us for the next game. Bye!

Danish: "Who has the job of picking the motm?!" -

commentTextItems.html: maiden ODI hundred for Muhammad Usman too..this was a full length delivery on the pads, driven straight down the ground and gets to his century..another good innings.
shortish delivery, backs away and mistimes the pull down the pitch
fuller around off, clipped away behind square leg

commentPreTextItems.html: George Macphers: "UAE have got this match in the bag with the help of a couple of late maximums. I think that Ireland were about 20-40 runs short of a defendable total. "

commentTextItems.html: another full toss toss, this time gets a leading edge to the push, on the bounce back towards the bowler
low full toss outside off, a lofted drive over the extra cover region for a boundary
full and slower, pushed down to long-off

commentTextItems.html: back of a length, taps it towards backward of point
length ball down leg side, clips it behind square leg for couple of runs
length ball outside off, pushed with soft hands to cover point
length ball on the pads, clipped past square leg
slower length ball, driven along the ground to wide of long-off
yorker length around off, gets an inside edge and ran across for a run

commentTextItems.html: short ball, outside off, pulls it through square leg, another boundary

fuller in length outside off, works it away to wide of third man fielder and gets a boundary

commentPreTextItems.html: Suku: "This match has produced a tight finish. And Best Scores for Rizwan,Usman, Best bowling figures for Campher."

commentTextItems.html: short ball, down leg side. Pulls it nicely off the back foot and sends it over the deep backward of square leg fence
shortish delivery down leg side, pulls it to fine leg
back of a length, just around off stump, beaten

milestones.description: Rizwan and Usman's 184-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 144 between Shaiman Anwar and Rameez Shahzad
Rizwan and Usman's 184-run partnership is UAE's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 160 between Shahzad and Khurram Khan
